  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Obdschu Schultt wiꞥſch\nſihdtiſs / to Glohdenu Dſellons\nwiꞥnu nokans.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tahs Uppes/ Straumes\nun Strautus no Meddus un\nStweesta wiꞥſch ne redſehs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Gann wiꞥſch strahdahß /\nbet no ta ne ko baudihß / zik\nwiꞥſch ceſpehs tik wiꞥſch atdohe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo wiꞥſch irr noſpaitijs\nun pamettis tohs Nabbagus /\nwiꞥſch irr Namums laupijs/ bet\ntas tohs ne uſtaisihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo wiꞥna Kungis ne bi-\nja piſdams/ wiꞥſch zaue fawu\nbaggatu Mantu ne taps iſ-\nglahbts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥnam ne aſlikke ne\nneeka/ ko warretu apr iht/ tadeht\nwiꞥna Labbums ne pataowehe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad wiꞥſch tchittids jew\npapillam eſſam / tad buhewi-\nnam Behdas / wiſſu Apb-hdi-\nnatu Rohka vahr wiꞥnu nahß.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas notiſs/ kad wiꞥſa\nKungis piſns tohp/tad (Deens)\nfawas Bahrsibas Karstunu\npahr wiꞥnu fuhtihs/ un liſs pawr\nwiꞥnu fawu Raufchanu lihtt\nliht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch behgs preekſch\ntahm Dſeſes Bruunahm / un\ntas Warra Stohps wiꞥnu zaue\nzaurnim fchaus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Schbins taps iſ-\nwilks/ un ees zaue wiꞥſa Mee-\nfahin ahra/ un ſpihdams Sch-\nbins tſees zaue wiꞥna Schul-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne kahta * Tumſibaia\nkaß wiꞥnu warretu apſleh-\nweens ne-uſpubſts Uaguns w\nzu aprths / ir tee Atlikkſc\nwiꞥna Dshwokli taps famaita\n* Eebr: Wall: Wiſa Tumſiba irr apſle\nta (jeb paturreta) preekſch wiꞥna apſle\nteem (Grebkeem:) tas iir, preekſch teem G\nkeem, ko wiꞥſch Sleppenſhâ darrijs, itr w\nnam tas Elles Ugguns jagaida.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta Debbes wiꞥna D\nseegumi finnamu darrihs/ uu\nGemme prett wiꞥnu zelfees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta Rohziba fawa Na-\nma aiſees/ (un wiſs) wiꞥna\niſſchkihdihß wiꞥna Duſinibe\nDeena.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schi irr weena beſdee-\nga Zilweka Dalta no Deewa/\nta Mantiba wiꞥna Slawas\nta STIPNA DEEWA.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Et Jiabs atbildeja/ u\nzazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Klausajt klausid\nni mannu Wallohu/ un lai\njuns par Eepreezinaſchanu irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pazeeschatees manni ru-\nnajht/ pehz apfineijeet gann t\ngi mannu Wallohu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Mannas Dohmas ne i\nzilweigas/ un ja tas ta irr/ k\npel\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
